entries.journal_entry_description: Valarian was able to get one of Jabba's men to sell information on a spice smuggling run. Jabba's lost a lot of money because of this and wants to find the culprit.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Your orders are to eliminate Valarian's supporters until you find a clue pointing to the informant. A few dead bodies should provide a deterrent to future leaks.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: A datadisk found on one of Valarian's former employees lists a time and location to get information on Jabba's next spice shipment. You are to attend that meeting instead and kill the informant.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: A datadisk found on one of Valarian's former employees lists a time and location to get information on Jabba's next spice shipment. You are to attend that meeting instead and kill the informant.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: The courier escaped. Bossk is not going to be happy about this.
